&lt;li&gt;Work hand-in-hand with product managers to understand customer and user needs, using this data and intuition to scope design work aligned with the product roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a mentor to junior designers, providing guidance and feedback in support of their growth.&lt;/li&gt;
