&lt;p&gt;Datacor&#39;s Lab Solutions Group delivers mission-critical LIMS and QC software to leading testing organizations, oil refineries, and chemical manufacturers globally. Our Bliss platform supports product quality, EPA adherence, and operational efficiency across complex multi-site lab environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are expanding our enterprise capability and growing our global client base. We&#39;re looking for someone who has worked inside TIC operations and can translate that experience into sales support and implementation success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will serve as a leading TIC industry SME on strategic enterprise engagements leading discovery, aligning platform capability to real-world TIC workflows, and building client-side ownership. When TIC project demand allows, you will operate as a full-cycle Implementation Specialist across our broader client portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role blends deep TIC industry credibility, LIMS implementation expertise, workflow analysis, and customer-facing leadership. Your value is your depth of real-world TIC knowledge and your ability to translate that into implementations that optimize the ROI for our clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TIC Industry SME:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
