&lt;li&gt;Serve as a primary TIC domain expert on enterprise client engagements the person in the room who makes lab leadership feel understood&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead structured discovery sessions with lab and quality managers, lab analysts and other stakeholders to document current-state workflows, pain points, and system requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Validate test method mappings, instrument configurations, and calculation logic against real lab outputs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop client super users and a client center of excellence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain the global lab rollout playbook each implementation should be faster and cleaner than the last&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Feed real-world TIC insights directly into product roadmap prioritization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
